        "paragraphs": [
          "Tarrant County is home to Fort Worth, Arlington, and many smaller communities across western DFW, where school districts and city boundaries can swing the total rate noticeably block by block.",
          "Comptroller-published total rates for each taxing unit are a practical starting point for comparing Fort Worth with Arlington or other cities before you account for exemptions and protest outcomes.",
          "Use the estimator to compare typical tax outcomes when you are deciding between neighborhoods or cities within the county.",
          "Enter your property value and pick a city when available to translate those rates into monthly and annual planning figures."
